<h1>Action Required: Complete Your Payment</h1>

<p>Hi <%= @user.email %>,</p>

<p>Congratulations! You won auction #<%= @auction.id %> with a winning bid of <strong>$<%= @amount_dollars %></strong>.</p>

<h2>Next Steps</h2>
<p>To complete your purchase, please proceed to payment within 48 hours:</p>

<div style="margin: 20px 0; padding: 15px; background-color: #f0f0f0; border-radius: 5px;">
  <p><strong>Amount Due:</strong> $<%= @amount_dollars %></p>
  <p><strong>Auction ID:</strong> <%= @auction.id %></p>
  <p><strong>Payment Deadline:</strong> 48 hours from now</p>
</div>

<p><a href="<%= root_url %>payments/<%= @payment_record.id %>" style="background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px;">Complete Payment</a></p>

<p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>The Auction Team</p>
